{"tid":1943000,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"建立「黃色經濟圈」最好嘅方法，並唔係幫趁黃店！","createTime":"2020-03-25T11:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T11:39:58.000Z","uid":21678,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"688cb039717abff22ba71cd5d6dc67b79b4711e9","tid":1943000,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:32:58.000Z","msg":"想拯救黃色經濟圈<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最有效嘅方法並唔係去黃店食多兩餐<br />\n而係要令到藍店執笠！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n因為藍店倒閉的話<br />\n佢哋原本食客可以提供嘅現金流<br />\n就會被同區黃店同中立店瓜分<br />\n<br />\n藍店死得愈多<br />\n黃店分到嘅新客就愈多<br />\n等同經濟上嘅草船借箭<br />\n<br />\n黃店得到嘅，唔單止係手足嘅支持<br />\n仲可以得到淺藍/中立撚嘅資金<br />\n一併去支撐黃店生存"},{"pid":"989efa4cbe90ebafad354b34323b8bf0cacf8b72","tid":1943000,"uid":21678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:34:02.000Z","msg":"食肆嘅本質<br />\n係為協助<br />\n1. 勞動人口<br />\n2. 旅客<br />\n呢兩群人嘅「煮食外判商」<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個群組以外嘅人<br />\n即係兒童、學生、煮婦同退休人士<br />\n對出外用餐嘅需求，相比之下非常之細<br />\n<br />\n如果我哋極端地簡化數據去分析<br />\n全香港10,000萬食肆<br />\n主要客戶群就係370萬勞動人口<br />\n以及平均每日香港「存放」住嘅100萬名遊客<br />\n<br />\n以2019統計<br />\nQ4當時旅客跌幅 3個月大約50%<br />\n而飲食業生意總額對比2018年同期少咗14.3%<br />\n所以呢個預估都幾make sense<br />\n<br />\n建基於呢個估算<br />\n因為封關少咗100萬旅客<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">整個飲食業要維持平均每間餐廳嘅生意量<br />\n就需要減少21% <br />\n即係大約2,000間嘅食肆</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"fcec0168d2296e8e8ba9890c1033b270b95adda7","tid":1943000,"uid":83543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:34:06.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n睇下樓主唔講裝修嘅話仲有咩招數可以玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93bfa22fccb2377feeff215032ede78f593a0636","tid":1943000,"uid":21678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:34:33.000Z","msg":"呢個情形就好似一間過度擴張嘅公司<br />\n去到爆煲一刻，需要裁員<br />\n<br />\n方案一<br />\n全民留職，但係就全體職員減兩成人工<br />\n方案二<br />\n炒走兩成人，而留低嘅人反而可以唔駛減人工<br />\n<br />\n個問題係<br />\n而家決定生殺大權嘅唔係HR<br />\n而係香港人"},{"pid":"38702d7282e14719ff3417b4919a7ed8bd56e41d","tid":1943000,"uid":51583,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:35:00.000Z","msg":"好多人唔爭氣藍到黑都照食<br />\n仲要好多年青人"},{"pid":"b0541cb81c95240a596306b9527a42299f7d3ec0","tid":1943000,"uid":14131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fcec0168d2296e8e8ba9890c1033b270b95adda7","tid":1943000,"uid":83543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:34:06.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n睇下樓主唔講裝修嘅話仲有咩招數可以玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:35:21.000Z","msg":"蟲系魔法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9088d44127c57a910d4807c04f44b8704a524b90","tid":1943000,"uid":149257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:37:52.000Z","msg":"推pi"},{"pid":"3aece0ccd93669610891f98af98f2d0a0834a3de","tid":1943000,"uid":21678,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:38:11.000Z","msg":"去到實際操作<br />\n要隊冧藍店<br />\n不外乎幫佢哋<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「開流」</span></span></strong>同<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「節源」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n(一) 開流<br />\n<br />\n1. 投訴、投訴、投訴<br />\n1823幫到你~~~<br />\n總之見到少少唔妥當<br />\n就唔好懶，一定要開1823個app 申張正義<br />\n搞到藍店老闆畀人投訴到懷疑人生<br />\n<br />\n2. 吸水珠珠大法<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uHz7wOR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuHz7wOR.gif&h=78bf3bf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n低成本低風險 攬炒方法  吸水珠珠塞爆渠！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1910461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1910461</a><br />\n呢個唔多講<br />\n對於有廁所嘅大酒樓，簡直係一擊必殺<br />\n<br />\n3. 紅裝修<br />\n呢個而家真係唔建議<br />\n因為示威次數減少，風險太高<br />\n手足請三思"},{"pid":"41fb48073dca238ec343f6a0f5f2c67f9fe85eae","tid":1943000,"uid":215861,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:40:47.000Z","msg":"其實唔食藍店已經夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa374987fd57dc0138f87b7e07ae0af9c384d93","tid":1943000,"uid":21678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:41:29.000Z","msg":"(二) 節源<br />\n<br />\n組織一個類似狙擊TVB/東方嘅群組<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">出任務畀手足去TripAdvisor / Google map / Openrice 寫藍店食評</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n食評一定要中肯<br />\n但係如果某啲食肆，衛生環境好有問題<br />\n就大家不妨影張靚相放上埋呢啲平台<br />\n一張照片更勝千言萬語<br />\n<br />\n呢個方法雖然未必影響到藍店呢一刻嘅生意<br />\n只係拖累將來少啲生客、同埋遊客區嘅舖會少啲外國遊客<br />\n<br />\n但係如果佢老闆感覺到個負評同民怨<br />\n儲吓儲吓去到不可控制嘅地步<br />\n（例如Google 得番2星, TripAdvisor 唔見咗影)<br />\n藍店老闆好可能會考慮「砍掉重練」<br />\n咁黃店就有機會"},{"pid":"ca3882583a4a7a5c07b15a61496bfe6d21063dc8","tid":1943000,"uid":87030,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:41:57.000Z","msg":"其實兩者無衝突<br />\n黃店經濟圈強個陣逆市就捱得住<br />\n弱個邊會比人淘汰<br />\n自由市場自然會選擇"},{"pid":"8d8c6f01fb763736497442b2285dbfe5135a15fa","tid":1943000,"uid":21678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"41fb48073dca238ec343f6a0f5f2c67f9fe85eae","tid":1943000,"uid":215861,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:40:47.000Z","msg":"其實唔食藍店已經夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:44:28.000Z","msg":"唔食就梗係啦<br />\n但係點樣畀到一個「絕望」嘅感覺畀藍店老闆<br />\n就要靠幫佢開流支源<br />\n<br />\n尤其係生意咁差<br />\n一個老闆考慮到個個月蝕十幾廿萬<br />\n如果要佢哋再投放更大賭注<br />\n正常人都會縮<br />\n寧願執咗佢先<br />\n咁樣黃店先可能有機可乘"},{"pid":"e05f7f38773401e9407d6f79821f1e47bf7a5b1e","tid":1943000,"uid":25170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fcec0168d2296e8e8ba9890c1033b270b95adda7","tid":1943000,"uid":83543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:34:06.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n睇下樓主唔講裝修嘅話仲有咩招數可以玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:46:15.000Z","msg":"1823 搞鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9820b2dd402e184f0805bdeca087f377170a7b2e","tid":1943000,"uid":21678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b0541cb81c95240a596306b9527a42299f7d3ec0","tid":1943000,"uid":14131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fcec0168d2296e8e8ba9890c1033b270b95adda7","tid":1943000,"uid":83543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:34:06.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n睇下樓主唔講裝修嘅話仲有咩招數可以玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:35:21.000Z","msg":"蟲系魔法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:46:58.000Z","msg":"呢個真係要好勇敢嘅手足先做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i1vEVYB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi1vEVYB.jpg&h=c0f1a510&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61c41c8e296b5f5bfe261472f8a339aaa36d9e33","tid":1943000,"uid":24345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca3882583a4a7a5c07b15a61496bfe6d21063dc8","tid":1943000,"uid":87030,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:41:57.000Z","msg":"其實兩者無衝突<br />\n黃店經濟圈強個陣逆市就捱得住<br />\n弱個邊會比人淘汰<br />\n自由市場自然會選擇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:48:43.000Z","msg":"有得加速嘅話緊係加速好，藍店越早收皮佢哋啲客源點都會釋放去第度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a88dcf1bdcb5335264018819346fdcbbf76fc0","tid":1943000,"uid":21678,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:50:54.000Z","msg":"食肆終極兢星　－　<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屎魔法！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我唔係屎魔法師，而係鍊金術師<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1702035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1702035</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XfdO4LY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXfdO4LY.png&h=ef54ec0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e4569e39bd048a346573770246d498c3b228113","tid":1943000,"uid":21678,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:03:10.000Z","msg":"最緊要嘅係<br />\n藍店老闆如果呢半年執笠<br />\n佢哋好大可能<br />\n就唔會再投廿蚊張<br />\n<br />\n一來藍老闆普遍戇鳩鳩<br />\n唔知道自己個一票功能組別票仍然有效；<br />\n<br />\n二來呢條張宇人<br />\n呢段時間冇好好做到佢飲食界議員嘅本分<br />\n派錢都派到一鑊粥咁<br />\n我係藍底都唔會撐佢"},{"pid":"13cc651985831eb8e91d9879b61dfa67d2d18fef","tid":1943000,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38702d7282e14719ff3417b4919a7ed8bd56e41d","tid":1943000,"uid":51583,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:35:00.000Z","msg":"好多人唔爭氣藍到黑都照食<br />\n仲要好多年青人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"實有呢啲人<br />\n所以要慢慢逐個擊破呢啲藍店<br />\n愈係多人<br />\n就愈值得收佢檔"},{"pid":"f1b9a6438506796d01495c5ea380a5cdfb0d65e7","tid":1943000,"uid":21678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:17:13.000Z","msg":"再者<br />\n一間食肆最惡頂嘅係租<br />\n冇事冇幹，業主係唔會主動減租嘅<br />\n<br />\n但係如果同一條街<br />\n有第二間藍店執笠<br />\n就係畀到黃店老闆最大嘅bargaining power 去要求業主減租<br />\n變相用咗藍店嘅血饅頭<br />\n去幫黃店節流"},{"pid":"c0bc0fcb442e01aef764aad00bd74ffd6de253a4","tid":1943000,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c100e4c0315bbeb87c6afeaee13441a006d0e2b","tid":1943000,"uid":41850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5083657b88ac729cb56f3b45c83488be3a4aca4","tid":1943000,"uid":37525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fcec0168d2296e8e8ba9890c1033b270b95adda7","tid":1943000,"uid":83543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:34:06.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n睇下樓主唔講裝修嘅話仲有咩招數可以玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:50:50.000Z","msg":"好多喎<br />\n走去藍page篤佢暗黃<br />\n請埋啲黃友做樓面<br />\n靜雞雞屌藍屍嘅<br />\n<br />\n唔夠藍<br />\n無講警甴加油<br />\n無貼毛筆開哂花嘅勁揪體<br />\n唔支持何君堯<br />\n門口無支持23條文宣<br />\n<br />\n總之用返而家鬥黃店<br />\n嘅準則同手法"},{"pid":"46721cb5df704874d20b8a30b7cf5838ccf6dad5","tid":1943000,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5083657b88ac729cb56f3b45c83488be3a4aca4","tid":1943000,"uid":37525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fcec0168d2296e8e8ba9890c1033b270b95adda7","tid":1943000,"uid":83543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:34:06.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n睇下樓主唔講裝修嘅話仲有咩招數可以玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:50:50.000Z","msg":"好多喎<br />\n走去藍page篤佢暗黃<br />\n請埋啲黃友做樓面<br />\n靜雞雞屌藍屍嘅<br />\n<br />\n唔夠藍<br />\n無講警甴加油<br />\n無貼毛筆開哂花嘅勁揪體<br />\n唔支持何君堯<br />\n門口無支持23條文宣<br />\n<br />\n總之用返而家鬥黃店<br />\n嘅準則同手法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:56:23.000Z","msg":"支持支持"},{"pid":"c68609a06437153dfb845ece0c244641fee6649d","tid":1943000,"uid":331551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"38702d7282e14719ff3417b4919a7ed8bd56e41d","tid":1943000,"uid":51583,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:35:00.000Z","msg":"好多人唔爭氣藍到黑都照食<br />\n仲要好多年青人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:57:20.000Z","msg":"真係唔明班後生仔諗咩<br />\n呢一兩餐飯可能斷送自己(子孫)既自由"},{"pid":"a084bf9dd53b9c4a8b3a7349ab605fbe09d79f38","tid":1943000,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c68609a06437153dfb845ece0c244641fee6649d","tid":1943000,"uid":331551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"38702d7282e14719ff3417b4919a7ed8bd56e41d","tid":1943000,"uid":51583,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:35:00.000Z","msg":"好多人唔爭氣藍到黑都照食<br />\n仲要好多年青人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T12:57:20.000Z","msg":"真係唔明班後生仔諗咩<br />\n呢一兩餐飯可能斷送自己(子孫)既自由"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:07:23.000Z","msg":"就係因為有呢啲人<br />\n先顯得消滅藍店重要<br />\n<br />\n呢啲所謂中立人士<br />\n去黃去藍，其實冇乜好惡<br />\n只係但求就手<br />\n只要佢去開嘅藍店收皮<br />\n自然焗住去黃店"}]}